<div class="row margin-top-medium dga-news-banner2">
    <div class="col-md-12 dga-news-banner-title"><h5>We are very pleased to announce for for a second straight year, Coach Adik has been awarded the <a href="/Content/images/Adik-Order-Sport-Excellence.jpg" target="_blank">Sport Manitoba Order of Sport Excellence</a> for his contributions to gymnastics in Manitoba!</h5></div>
