<div class="row margin-top-medium">
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <h3>About Us</h3>
        <h6 class="margin-top-medium">Dakota Gymnastics Academy Offers:</h6>
        <ol class="margin-top-small">
            <li>Instruction by NCCP certified coaches</li>
            <li>Structured and challenging programs</li>
            <li>Safe, fun and positive environment</li>
        </ol>
        <p>@Html.ActionLink("More About Us »", "About", "Home", null, new { @class = "" })</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <h3>Why Gymnastics?</h3>
        <p>Gymnastics is considered a foundational sport by the International Olympic committee. Athletes will develop:</p>
        <ol class="margin-top-medium">
            <li>Strength, flexibility and discipline</li>
            <li>Confidence and positive mental health</li>
            <li>Work ethic and discipline</li>
            <li>Exceptional fitness and much more</li>
        </ol>
        <p>@Html.ActionLink("Learn More »", "About", "Home", null, null, "whygymnastics", null, null)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <h3>Programs</h3>
        <p>Dakota Gymnastics Academy offers a wide variety of programs from parent-and-tots to competitive gymnastics. Our programming centres around four popular gymnastics disciplines: women’s artistic gymnastics, men’s artistic gymnastics, acrobatic gymnastics, and gym-for-all.</p>
        <p>@Html.ActionLink("More Information »", "Index", "Programs", null, null)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <h3>Registration</h3>
        <p>Winter registration is ongoing so why wait for spring – start today! Please read the information on the registration page to understand how to register and our payment/refund policy.</p>
        <p>If you are already familiar with how to register and our policies, you can download and print the <a href="@PdfForm" target="_blank">Registration Form</a> and register today!</p>
        <p>@Html.ActionLink("More Information »", "Index", "Registration", null, null)</p>
    </div>
</div>

